           <lg n="1" met="āryā">
           <l n="ab" real="+++++--+++++-+-+---"><lb n="1"/>ye dhammā hetu-prabhavā <space/> tesaṁ hetuṁ tathāgato Avaca</l>
           <l n="cd"><lb n="2"/>tesañ ca yo nirodho <space/> Evaṁ-vādī mahā-samano</l>
           </lg>
