	<div type="translation" source="bib:Skilling2019_01">
           <p rend="stanza" n="1">The states arisen from a cause / Their cause the Tathāgata proclaims, / As well as their cessation: This is the teaching of the Great Ascetic.</p>
	</div>
         <div type="translation" source="bib:Coedes1937-1966_01" xml:lang="fra">
           <p>Les conditions qui proviennent d'une cause, d'elles le Tathāgata a dit la cause, d'elles aussi ce qui est la suppression. Telle est la doctrine du Grand Ascète.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The French translation is c.</p>
         </div>
